{"tid":2068920,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華憂印美俄聯手 收口免被圍攻","createTime":"2020-06-18T04:41:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T09:01:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":130,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":100,"replies":[{"pid":"531a1ff9511c1bed17068d264960f40e211dee37","tid":2068920,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:41:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200618/SBWKB7VS7NFDVTASD2USIBL5JQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200618%2FSBWKB7VS7NFDVTASD2USIBL5JQ%2F&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wT4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=5325f1fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200618%2FSBWKB7VS7NFDVTASD2USIBL5JQ%2F&h=fb19789d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200618/SBWKB7VS7NFDVTASD2USIBL5JQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n華憂印美俄聯手 收口免被圍攻<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/tVj62xLYzviE8r0b_kZnFHwVtwE=/802x540/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SF4XHZNHBB4TNIWRWCGVZFWUQE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FtVj62xLYzviE8r0b_kZnFHwVtwE%3D%2F802x540%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSF4XHZNHBB4TNIWRWCGVZFWUQE.jpg&h=12ba7f85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n莫迪稱不會白費士兵的犧牲。<br />\n<br />\n【拆局】現時印度殺氣騰騰，中國顯得龜縮退避。中國政策科學研究會高級研究員、軍事文化研究會特聘軍事專家王雲飛撰文認為印度的進取是出於誤判，以為印軍比中國軍隊強，中國受制美國不敢回擊印度。時事評論員劉銳紹向本報指，中國的退讓及不公開傷亡，是希望避免刺激國內民族主義，「公開戰況可能帶來更大負面影響」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：有默契不用槍械 被嘲石器戰爭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n受制疫情再爆內憂<br />\n<br />\n王雲飛認為印度咄咄逼人源於一系列誤判，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。王強調印度這些判斷無理，原因是「無論從戰略環境還是從國力、軍力來分析，印度挑起戰爭將必敗無疑。」<br />\n<br />\n劉銳紹指出，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。至於中國不公開死傷，他認為若外媒死傷報道屬實，中國死傷高於印度，避免刺激國內的民族主義，「不少人懷疑解放軍能不能打仗，如果公開戰績，將帶來更大負面形響。」<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者"},{"pid":"36c8e9f439ed28dd3a4bd5b8554b911b5dd46d1b","tid":2068920,"uid":21545,"like":107,"dislike":2,"score":105,"